room_title: Escape room "The Collector's Warehouse" by Locked In Stuart in West Palm Beach
room_description: The long forgotten Collector's Warehouse has finally been found. You and your team have been given 60 minutes to locate the fabled Chalice of Zurbane. This famed collection is rumored to hold the world's most exquisite and obscure antiquities. These collectibles have been gathered, curated, and protected for more than five centuries. Handle them with care, but be quick, this is your only chance at obtaining the Chalice and escaping.
